{"title":"江上送粮船","authors":["王冬雪","赵志方"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上送粮船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝蓝的天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔江水过三关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧波红光十八湾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸竹林橘子树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅美景好江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上下来了运粮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔家的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上的帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水红阳金灿灿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲高歌总路线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双桨荡水琴弦动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声委婉江上传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江心过来了运粮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船连着船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船上的粮食千万石。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送得太阳落了山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月值班东山起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上龙舟望无边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽是运粮的船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社红旗迎风展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党栽花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船花朵朵片片帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社的红线长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的领导就是钢针尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿起了江上的运粮船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王冬雪诗  赵志方画（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}